text: Madhusmita Somnath Behera (born 4 October 1990 at Cuttack, Orissa) is an Odia cricketer. She is a right-handed batsman and bowls right-arm off-break. She plays for Odisha and East Zone. She has played 8 First-class, 71 List A and 43 Women's Twenty20. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Odisha women cricketers Category:East Zone women cricketers Category:Living people
